          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>From these paintings, our team has done what we do best: transform artistic expression into wearable joy. But here’s the twist — no two shoes are alike. Each pair is cut from a different part of the final artwork. Every brushstroke, shape, and hue is placed randomly on fabric, making each product a singular fragment of the original canvas. The result? A limited-edition collection where art doesn’t just walk — it lives, breathes, and dances.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
