    "7abbacd2-0a23-4678-b6c5-7e466e2c9483": {
      "type": "custom-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "template--18940872589656__7abbacd2-0a23-4678-b6c5-7e466e2c9483-1683817316951370c5-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This second edition isn’t about repetition. It’s about evolution. It’s about capturing the rawness of Atanásio’s themes — whether that’s the nostalgia of childhood, the permission to be fully yourself, or the pursuit of peace in chaos — and delivering them in ways that are tactile, intimate, and completely unique. Just like the paintings, the shoes invite interpretation. And just like the artist, the wearer becomes the storyteller.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
