        "text_8yKDCX": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Guilherme (or just Atanásio as we like to call him) is a young Portuguese abstract painter based in Lisbon, known for his vibrant, movement-rich canvases that often incorporate mantras and explore themes of presence and the complexity of emotional and human expression. After completing a master's degree in Electrical and Computer Engineering in 2021, he transitioned fully into painting, living his dream, developing his skills through self-guided experimentation, and inspired by the beauty of the world. His work has gained significant traction on social media, leading to collaborations with brands like Paez and Coca-Cola, and exhibitions such as \"We Came Here To Feel Good\" in 2023. </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
